Might need another one.

310
00:19:04.344 --> 00:19:06.146
[laughing]
Might need another one.

311
00:19:06.213 --> 00:19:08.148
You got it.

312
00:19:12.887 --> 00:19:14.055
Ah. you got him.

313
00:19:14.122 --> 00:19:16.356
-Damn.
-[phone buzzing]

