338
00:20:11.079 --> 00:20:13.313
♪ somber music ♪

339
00:20:34.068 --> 00:20:36.369
♪♪♪

340
00:21:00.661 --> 00:21:02.329
Tell me to shut up if you want.

341
00:21:02.395 --> 00:21:05.265
