<i>My old man always said.</i>

370
00:23:31.779 --> 00:23:33.480
"The surer a man is.
the less he knows."

371
00:23:33.547 --> 00:23:36.083
Hector wasn't wrong.

372
00:23:36.150 --> 00:23:37.718
So how can anyone be sure

373
00:23:37.785 --> 00:23:39.520
