451
00:33:11.726 --> 00:33:13.260
[Carter]
That's a...

452
00:33:13.327 --> 00:33:16.263
That's a full-blooded
African leopard.

453
00:33:17.532 --> 00:33:19.199
Holy shit.

454
00:33:22.236 --> 00:33:24.706
