507
00:37:21.709 --> 00:37:23.745
Okay.

508
00:37:23.811 --> 00:37:28.750
[scoffs] Take my fucking truck.
See about that.

509
00:37:37.424 --> 00:37:39.994
-Move.
-Where you going?

510
00:37:40.061 --> 00:37:41.562
None of your fucking business.

511
00:37:41.629 --> 00:37:43.164
